Description: Papyrus fragment bearing 19 lines of a Coptic text written against the fibres (recto) and Two line Coptic and an Arabic text written on the back, along the fibres (recto).
Curator's comments: Under study by Adrienn Almasy with a view to publication.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380836) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380836)
